Y|year=1994|title=The Boatmen of Thessaloniki: The Anarchist Bulgarian Group and the Bombing Actions of 1903|publisher= Trochalia (in Greek)|isbn=9789607022479|ref=harv}}\n*{{cite book | last=Moran | first=Matthew | last2=Waddington | first2=David | title=Riots | chapter=Neoliberalism, Austerity, and Rage Against the State: The Greek Riots of 2008 | publisher=Palgrave Macmillan UK | location=London | year=2016 | isbn=978-1-137-57130-4 | doi=10.1057/978-1-137-57131-1_5 | ref=harv}}\n*{{cite book|last=Moskoff|first=Kostis|authorlink=:el:\u039a\u03c9\u03c3\u03c4\u03ae\u03c2 \u039c\u03bf\u03c3\u03ba\u03ce\u03c6|trans-title=An introduction to the history of the working class movement|title=\u0395\u03b9\u03c3\u03b1\u03b3\u03c9\u03b3\u03b9\u03ba\u03ac \u03c3\u03c4\u03b7\u03bd \u03b9\u03c3\u03c4\u03bf\u03c1\u03af\u03b1 \u03c4\u03bf\u03c5 \u03ba\u03b9\u03bd\u03ae\u03bc\u03b1\u03c4\u03bf\u03c2 \u03c4\u03b7\u03c2 \u03b5\u03c1\u03b3\u03b1\u03c4\u03b9\u03ba\u03ae\u03c2 \u03c4\u03ac\u03be\u03b7\u03c2|lang=el|publisher=\u039a\u03b1\u03c3\u03c4\u03b1\u03bd\u03b9\u03ce\u03c4\u03b7\u03c2 |location=Athens |year= 1985|edition=2nd|isbn=9789600300703|oclc=1039058446|ref=harv}}\n*{{cite book |last1=Roos |first1=J\u00e9r\u00f4me E. |last2=Oikonomakis |first2=Leonidas |chapter=They Don't Represent Us! The Global Resonance of the Real Democracy Movement from the Indignados to Occupy |pp=117\u2013136 |editor-last1=Porta|editor-first1=Donatella della|editor-last2=Mattoni|editor-first2=Alice|title=Spreading Protest: Social Movements in Times of Crisis|chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=k5yCBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA127|year=2014|publisher=ECPR Press|isbn=978-1-910259-20-7|ref=harv}}\n* {{Cite book |editor-last1=Schwarz |editor-first1=A. G |editor-last2=Sagris |editor-first2=Tasos |editor3=Void Network |title=We Are an Image from the Future: The Greek Revolt of December 2008 |date=2010 |chapter=These Days Are for Alexis; Chronology: December 6\u201325, 2008 |pp=77\u201381 |ol=24604918M |language=